{"tid":2280690,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登團隊未獲准進入聯邦機構","createTime":"2020-11-10T15:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T06:44:39.000Z","uid":184679,"like":177,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"3fd29a87e8926aab924db670565547880a6f6e14","tid":2280690,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T15:52:26.000Z","msg":"宣布勝出美國總統大選的拜登, 仍然未獲聯邦總務署確認為總統當選人, 團隊人員未獲批准進入聯邦機構. 拜登團隊向傳媒表示, 由於交接工作受阻, 可能會提出法律訴訟, 但強調未有決定, 仍有其他方法處理問題.<br />\n<br />\n        至於總統特朗普仍未承認落敗, 特朗普的競選陣營發動法律戰.<br />\n<br />\n        特朗普不認輸, 令到政府軍心不穩, 司法部批准聯邦檢察官調查選舉有無不尋常後, 一名司法部官員懷疑不滿有關政策而辭職. 另外特朗普突然宣布開除國防部長埃斯珀的職務.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20201110233655\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsID%3D20201110233655&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7IiLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=02a0e3c9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20201110233655</a>"},{"pid":"af39fb2c1c6610a2a1f33452b93df1ae0c82a59f","tid":2280690,"uid":370061,"like":175,"dislike":1,"score":174,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T15:54:41.000Z","msg":"邊位啊，冇人識你喎，見主任就拎籌排隊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a608c339a099638d617db780f020aea73f2470","tid":2280690,"uid":54125,"like":114,"dislike":1,"score":113,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T15:55:49.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">拜登團隊向傳媒表示, 由於交接工作受阻, 可能會提出法律訴訟, 但強調未有決定, 仍有其他方法處理問題.</span><br />\n<br />\n唔係唔告下wa<br />\n唔告正契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw垃圾報又係偏頗到嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee2c2179744efd48ccee675ccfdbd47b3d880e94","tid":2280690,"uid":22700,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T16:34:59.000Z","msg":"淨係急住奪權 <br />\n拜登團隊好似冇提過話冇選舉舞幣"},{"pid":"f6d5ca811efd83131fc99fbfd119502cd196ec11","tid":2280690,"uid":287577,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,